Privacy Policy for GC Gold Rate

Effective Date: [01/01/2025]  
Last Updated: [01/04/2025]

At GC Gold Rate, your privacy is our priority. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application and related services (collectively, the “App”). Please read this policy carefully to understand our views and practices regarding your personal data.

---

Information We Collect

We collect the following categories of information:

Personal Information
User account details (e.g., name, email address)

Third-Party Information
Information collected via APIs (e.g., real-time gold rates, news sources)
Authentication tokens (e.g., Google/Apple Sign-In)

Data Sharing and Disclosure

We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. However, we may share limited data with:
Service providers assisting with analytics, hosting, or push notifications
Regulatory bodies, if required by law


All third-party access is governed by contractual confidentiality and data processing agreements.

Security Measures

We implement industry-standard safeguards to protect your data, including:

- Encryption in transit and at rest
- Secure server environments
- Access controls and user authentication

However, please note that no system is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

User Rights

Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:

- Access, correct, or delete your data
- Object to or restrict data processing
- Withdraw consent for data collection
- File a complaint with a data protection authority

To exercise these rights, contact us at: forlogin.cs@gmail.com

Children’s Privacy

The App is not intended for users under the age of 13 (or equivalent age as per local regulations). We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.


Third-Party Links and Services

The App may contain links to third-party websites or services . We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these entities and encourage users to review their privacy policies independently.

Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any material changes will be notified through the App or via email (if available). Continued use of the App indicates your acceptance of the updated policy.

Contact Us

If you have any questions, concerns, or requests related to this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

GC Gold Rate
Email: [forlogin.cs@gmail.com]  
